p.s:
The guide was supplemented with tutorials on the use of H5P (
https://h5p.org/
) , a plugin for publishing systems that makes it easy to create , share and reuse highly interactive web content .

Working on the Drupal content management system (
https://www.drupal.org
) , these tutorials empowered the collaborating doctors , content producers and ESL interpreters to create rich materials efficiently , out of a sizeable set of content types and templates .
